PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2001-11902001-06-280,  HERITAGE,  ,  , 
PrecisAppointment of FRANÇOIS MACEROLA, of Outremont, Quebec, as a member of the Canadian Film Development Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending February 17, 2002, in the place of Laurier L. LaPierre, who has resigned; and designation of FRANÇOIS MACEROLA as Chairperson of the Canadian Film Development Corporation; effective July 4, 2001.
